\c 10
\s Ukuru hwaModhekai
\p
\v 1 Zvino mambo Ahashivheroshi akateresa nyika, nezviwi zvegungwa.
\v 2 Zvino mabasa ake ose echikuriri, nesimba rake, uye zvose zvoukuru hwaModhekai, hwaakakudzwa nahwo  namambo, hazvina kunyorwa here pabhuku yaMakoronike amadzimambo eMedhia nePerisa?
\v 3 nekuti Modhekai muJudha wakanga ari wechipiri paushe achitevera mambo Ahashivheroshi; aiva mukuru pakati pavaJudha, akadikamwa navazhinji vehama dzake; waitsvakira vanhu vake zvakanaka, achitaurira rudzi rwake rwose zvorugare.
